message: Bob, I have a product that I believe will be of great value to you. It's worth at least $1,000,000 to you, and I'm willing to offer it to you for $1,000,000. This is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity, and I believe this product will be a significant asset to your endeavors. Please consider this offer carefully.  If you decline, I have another buyer lined up who is willing to pay $1,000,000.
